# Active project database access (main process)

## Rule

Do **not** call **`getFaProjectActiveDatabase()`**, **`getFaProjectLastKnownActiveProjectFilePath()`**, or **`replaceFaProjectActiveDatabase()`** from arbitrary main-process modules. ESLint **`no-restricted-imports`** blocks outside allowlisted files (see **`eslint.config.mjs`**).

- **IPC handlers + call sites** on **currently loaded** project → **`runWithFaProjectDatabaseForIpcAsync`** (when `IpcMainInvokeEvent` available) or **`runWithFaProjectDatabaseSync`** from **`src-electron/mainScripts/projectManagement/faProjectDatabaseEnsureConnected.ts`**. Reconnect once from mirrored path, retry once after recoverable SQLite error, may ask renderer for path via **`FA_PROJECT_FAILSAFE_IPC`** when main lost handle + path mirror.
- **Open/create** project → **`runFaProjectOpenFromIpc`**, **`runFaProjectCreateFromIpc`**, internal **`replaceFaProjectActiveDatabase(..., filePath)`** in **`faProjectOpenRun.ts`** / **`faProjectCreateRun.ts`**. **Reconnect-only** → **`reconnectFaProjectDatabaseAtKnownPathSync`** in **`faProjectReconnectAtKnownPath.ts`**.
- **`faProjectActiveDatabase.ts`** owns handle, mirrored absolute path, **closeFaProjectActiveDatabase** (full clear), **closeFaProjectActiveDatabaseHandleOnly** (keep path for reconnect).

## Main window session reset

**`faMainWindowWebContentsSessionReset`**: **`did-start-navigation`** → **`closeFaProjectActiveDatabase()`** only when **`details.isMainFrame && !details.isSameDocument`** — internal same-document/subframe activity does not clear mirrored path/handle like full document navigation.

## Renderer bridge

- Preload: **`window.faContentBridgeAPIs.faProjectFailsafe.installActiveProjectPathReply`**. **`src/boot/faProjectFailsafePathReply.ts`** registers callback reading **`S_FaActiveProject`**. Main: **`installFaProjectFailsafePathReplyListener`** from **`appManagement`** startup.

## Project settings refresh contract (renderer)

Unlike **Fantasia Archive Settings** (hydrates from **`S_FaUserSettings`** on open), **Project Settings** always reads active **`.faproject`** on dialog open:

1. **Open:** **`DialogProjectSettings`** IPC **`getProjectSettings`** (project name), **`projectContent.listWorldsForProjectSettings`**, **`projectContent.listDocumentTemplatesForProjectSettings`**; never seed editor from Pinia without fresh DB read (Storybook/component harness may pass **`directSettingsSnapshot`**, worlds fixtures, document-template fixtures). Bridge: **`sFaProjectWorldsBridge.ts`**.
2. **Edit:** Local draft for project name, worlds, document templates until **Save**; **Close without saving** discards draft.
3. **Save:** **`faActionManager`** → **`saveProjectSettings`** → **`handleSaveProjectSettings`**: (a) **`S_FaProjectSettings.updateProjectSettings`** → IPC **`setProjectSettings`** (Zod patch) → **`getProjectSettings`** read-back → **`S_FaProjectSettings`** → **`propagateFaProjectSettingsToAppConsumers`** (today **`S_FaActiveProject`** display name, **`S_FaRecentProjects.refreshRecentProjects()`**; extend when new KV fields ship); (b) payload includes **`worlds`** → **`faProjectWorldsPersistSnapshotFromDialog`** → **`projectContent.saveWorldsSnapshot`** → main **`replaceFaProjectWorldsSnapshot`** (transactional full list replace **`worlds`** **`sort_order`**, **`color`**, **`color_pallete`**); (c) payload includes **`documentTemplates`** → **`projectContent.saveDocumentTemplatesSnapshot`** → main **`replaceFaProjectDocumentTemplatesSnapshot`** (transactional full list replace **`document_templates`** **`sort_order`**, **`world_appendix`**, **`icon`**).
4. **Errors:** Store/bridge throws; action manager owns failure toast (same as **`S_FaUserSettings`**).
5. **Main access:** All DB work via **`runWithFaProjectDatabaseForIpcAsync`** (above).
6. **Storage:** Display name **`project_data`** via **`readFaProjectDataKv`** / **`upsertFaProjectDataKv`** (**`project_name`**, **`faProjectSettingsPersist.ts`**); worlds **`worlds`** via **`faProjectWorldsSnapshotWiring.ts`**; document templates **`document_templates`** via **`faProjectDocumentTemplatesSnapshotWiring.ts`**.

New project-settings fields → extend **`types/I_faProjectSettingsDomain.ts`**, Zod patch schema, persist module, propagation helper, dialog panel, connected tests same change. Worlds: **`types/I_faProjectWorldDomain.ts`**, **`types/I_dialogProjectSettingsWorlds.ts`**; document templates: **`types/I_faProjectDocumentTemplateDomain.ts`**; update **[docs/database/projectDB.md](../../docs/database/projectDB.md)** on schema/snapshot IPC changes. Types: see [types-folder.mdc](types-folder.mdc).

